What is your overall assessment of this course?
Do you expect to use this class for credit toward your major, or toward a pre-professional program?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Naval Science 100 01 was an extension of the Intro to Naval Science class offered for ROTC Midshipmen, and allowed for more hands-on learning in contrast with the classroom work involved in the Intro class. I would recommend the class simply because it is a necessary component of the ROTC course list.
